description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured the return of Eileen, Camille, Adrienne, Brandi, Kim, Kris Jenner, Kathy Hilton, GLENN the party planner and more! On The Real Housewives of New York, RHONY whiplash strikes the Berkshires, plus an appearance from our Yummie Tummy mama Heather Holla Thomson!


RHONY Recap: 26:50ish


WATCH a brand-new interview with Mindy Cohn (Facts of Life) on YouTube at YouTube.com/DannyPellegrino1
